title: Lag Without High Ping
body:
I came home went for a match,everything was cool till min 6 ( the moment i ganked ) than game lagged for no real reason at all! Like i have 90ms fix and if it even goes beyond that it than goes down in 1 second.It just happened today is there a solution to solve this?Please help
{{sticker:cass-cry}}

replies.body: If it stutters randomly like that, it kinda makes me think you might have some packet loss issues. Grab the network logs from that game if you can and have our [**log reader**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209765743) scan it. Paste an image of what it gives you here so I can take a look with you!
